data.description: This immaculately maintained 5 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home is nestled in the highly sought-after Phase IV of the Shaw Woods subdivision, located along the Etowah River. This stunning custom beauty sits on a rare sprawling acre lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. Positioned on a serene cul-de-sac, this home offers retreat, with space to grow.    Access the main level of the home, which shines with beautiful hardwood flooring, from either the wrap-around front porch or the spacious two-car garage - a rare find in the neighborhood. As you step into the two-story foyer adorned with a grand chandelier, you'll be greeted by stairs leading to the upper level where four bedrooms, including the generously-sized master bedroom, await. Alternatively, you can enter the dining room that comfortably accommodates 12 guests. Adjacent to the foyer, you'll find the inviting living room and a convenient half-bath.    The kitchen boasts sleek stainless steel gas cooking appliances, a state-of-the-art Samsung refrigerator, and a spacious island that comfortably accommodates up to six people. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a cozy sitting area with a gas fireplace, perfect for informal gatherings. Additionally, the kitchen seamlessly connects to the inviting eat-in breakfast spaces. The living area, adorned with expansive windows offering picturesque views of the backyard, features a second gas-powered fireplace with gas logs.    In addition to this level, there is a walk-out covered and screened-in patio that opens up to a newly painted open deck. It's perfect for sunbathing, gardening, entertaining, or simply relishing in the beauty of nature from your own backyard.    The master bedroom and ensuite bathroom feature elegant tray ceilings. Unwind in a luxurious whirlpool tub and relish the convenience of a spacious dual vanity and oversized his and her closets. On the upper level, you'll find a laundry room and three guest rooms, along with an additional full bath. All bedrooms are equipped with brand-new ceiling fans.    Enjoy direct access to the fully finished walk-out, daylight basement from the living area. With LVP flooring throughout, there's plenty of room to customize the space to meet your specific needs, including the option for a bedroom. You'll also find a full bath with a  shower/tub combo in the basement. Rest easy during inclement weather with the dedicated storm shelter, which also provides extra storage space. Step outside to the fenced backyard through the deck connected to the basement.     Surrounded by evergreens, this home boasts year-round landscaping. During the warmer months, the yard flourishes with apple trees, strawberry and blueberry gardens, and charming rose bushes. The warmer months also give transformation to the wooded backyard - fresh leaves add privacy and vibrant colors. Follow the private rock-lined trail that traces the rear property line, and immerse yourself in nature's tranquil beauty directly from your back porch. The spacious backyard provides a well-maintained, fenced area, perfect for keeping pets and children safe. Additionally, a storage shed is available to conveniently store lawn care and gardening tools.    Impressive upgrades and updates comprise a new roof and gutters, only two years young. The residence is now equipped with a smart home thermostat system, catering to all three zones. Additionally, fresh paint adorns every level, both inside and out, while the driveway and sidewalk have been thoroughly pressure washed. A transferable home warranty through American Home Shield will be provided.  The neighborhood offers numerous amenities, including well-maintained sidewalks, street lighting, two pools, a scenic nature walk along the Etowah River, and plans for constructing a playground.
